{"tid":2075980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 010】亂世中，如何做良心公務員？","createTime":"2020-06-23T07:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T07:43:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73c946350c8b0c656e0eded2dd23da4e9060be65","tid":2075980,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"0:01 / 25:02<br />\n<br />\n【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 010】亂世中，如何做良心公務員？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPDISL3b5HU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOPDISL3b5HU&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=7449d8d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPDISL3b5HU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n111K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n香港進入大黑暗時期，各行各業無不要面對「新常態」，包括香港全體公務員。究竟要當一個良心公務員，可以如何自處？在過去一年，組織公務員罷工集會公投的新公務員工會主席顏武周備受壓力，明知道可預見的風險，依然無怨無悔，經歷了哪些心路歷程？我們也邀請了曾為曾俊華助選的前AO Kennon，比較兩代公務員文化的差異。在新香港，受到打壓的都是有良心、有理想、有承擔的時代精英，同路人好應該互相扶持，直到光復一天。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=c7a6d7d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5c073271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8672c32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/simonshen</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simons